        <p class="mb-4">It all started when a group of college students realized they were collectively spending hundreds of dollars every month on overlapping subscriptions. They thought: "What if we could share these services legally and securely?"</p>
        <p>Today, SubSplit has grown into a trusted platform connecting thousands of users who want to access premium content without premium prices. Our mission remains the same: making digital services accessible to everyone.</p>
