            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">For Subscribers</h4>
              <p>SubSplit lets you browse available subscription slots from verified hosts. Choose from hundreds of plans across streaming, music, productivity, and more — and pay only for your share. No more full-price subscriptions for services you use occasionally.</p>
              <ul class="list-unstyled mt-4">
