                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Pay securely through our integrated wallet</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm p-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">For Hosts</h4>
              <p>Have unused slots in your family plan? SubSplit helps you monetize them safely. List your available slots, set your price, and connect with verified subscribers. Our platform handles payments, notifications, and ensures smooth sharing.</p>
              <ul class="list-unstyled mt-4">
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Recover costs from your existing subscriptions</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Manage all your shared plans in one dashboard</li>
                <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check-circle text-primary me-2"></i> Get automatic payments with no hassle</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

